quran[564]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Kodi akufunsana nkhani zotani
  78,2,Ali kufunsana za nkhani ija yaikulu
  78,3,Nkhani imene akusiyana maganizo pakati pawo
  78,4,"Iyayi, iwo adzadziwa posachedwa"
  78,5,"Iyayi, iwo adzadziwa posachedwapa"
  78,6,Kodi Ife sitidapange dziko lapansi monga ngati kama
  78,7,Ndi mapiri ngati zikhomo
  78,8,Ndipo Ife tidakulengani inu awiri awiri
  78,9,Ndipo tidapanga tulo kukhala ngati mpumulo wanu
  78,10,Ndipo tidapanga usiku kukhala chophimba
  78,11,Ndipo tinapanga usana kukhala kopezera zofuna zanu
  78,12,Ndipo tidamanga mlengalenga miyamba isanu ndi iwiri
  78,13,Ndipo tidakhazikitsa mmenemo nyali yowala
  78,14,Ndipo tidatumiza mvula yambiri kuchokera ku mitambo ya mvula
  78,15,Kuti timeretse chakudya ndi mbewu
  78,16,Ndipo minda ya zomera zothinana
  78,17,Ndithudi tsiku la chiweruzo lidakhazikitsidwa kale
  78,18,Tsiku limene lipenga lidzalira ndipo inu mudzadza mu magulumagulu
  78,19,Ndipomumlengalengamudzatsegulidwa ndipo mudzakhala ngati makomo
  78,20,Ndipo mapiri onse adzayendetsedwa ndi kukhala ngati nthunzi yamadzi
  78,21,Ndithudi Gahena ili kuwayembekezera
  78,22,Mudzi wa anthu ophwanya malamulo
  78,23,Kumeneko ndiko kumene adzakhale mpaka kalekale
  78,24,Kumeneko sadzalawa chozizira kapena kumwa china chilichonse
  78,25,"Kupatula Al-Naba\t637 madzi owira ndi mafinya"
  78,26,Mphotho yoyeneradi
  78,27,"Chifukwa, ndithudi, iwo sanali kuopa chidzudzulo chathu"
  78,28,Ndipo iwo moyerekedwa anali kukana chivumbulutso chathu
  78,29,Ndipo Ife tidalemba m’Buku zonse zimene anali kuchita
  78,30,Motero inu lawani! Inu simudzalandira china chilichonse koma manzunzo ochuluka
  78,31,Ndithudi kwa anthu oopa Mulungu kudzakhala kupambana
  78,32,Minda ndi m’minda ya mphesa
  78,33,Ndi a namwali akulu akulu ofanana zaka
  78,34,Ndi chikho chodzadza
  78,35,Kumeneko iwo sadzamva mawu opanda pake kapena nkhani zabodza
  78,36,Imeneyi ndiyo mphotho yochokera kwa Ambuye wako ndipo ndi mphotho yokwanira
  78,37,"Ambuye wa Kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili pakati pawo, Mwini chisoni chosatha ndipo iwo sadzatha kulankhula naye"
  78,38,Patsiku limene Mzimu ndi angelo adzaima pa mizere ndipo palibe amene adzalankhula kupatula yekhayo amene adzalandira chilolezo cha Mwini chifundo chosatha ndipo adzanena chinthu chimene chili choona
  78,39,"Ndithudi tsiku limeneli ndi loona, motero iye amene afuna, mulekeni atsatire njira yobwerera kwa Ambuye wake"
  78,40,"Ndithudi takuchenjezani za chilango chowawa chimene chili nkudza posachedwa. Tsiku limene munthu adzayang’ana ntchito zimene manja ake adatsogoza, ndipo osakhulupirira adzati: “Kalanga ine, ndikanakhala dothi.”"
  79,1,Pali iwo amene amalanda mwankhanza
  79,2,Ndi pali iwo amene amachotsa mwaufulu
  79,3,Ndi pali iwo amene amauluka
  79,4,Ndi pali iwo amene amathamanga ngati ali pa liwiro loopsya
  79,5,Ndi pali angelo amene amakwaniritsa kuchita malamulo a Ambuye wawo
  79,6,Patsiku limene dziko ndi mapiri zidzagwedezeka kwambiri
  79,7,Ndi kulira kwa lipenga kawiri
  79,8,"Mitima, patsiku limeneli, idzafumuka ndi kuda nkhawa"
  79,9,Maso awo atagwetsa pansi
  79,10,"Iwo amanena kuti: “Kodi ife tidzabwerera monga momwe tinali poyamba?”"
  79,11,“Angakhale mafupa athu ataola?”
  79,12,"Iwo amati: “Kubwerera kotero ndi kopanda phindu.”"
  79,13,Koma udzakhala mfuwu umodzi okha
  79,14,"Pamene, taona, iwo adzadzipeza okha ali pamwamba pa nthaka ali ndi moyo"
  79,15,Kodiinumudaimvankhaniya Mose
  79,16,PameneAmbuye wake adamuitana mu dambo lodalitsika la Tuwa
  79,17,“Pita kwa Farao; Ndithudi iye waphwanya malamulo mopyola muyezo.”
  79,18,"“Ndipo ukamuuze kuti: Kodi ungadziyeretse wekha?”"
  79,19,“Ndi kuti ine ndikulondolere kwa Ambuye wako kuti uzimuopa Iye?”
  79,20,Kotero iye adamuonetsa chizindikiro cha chikulu
  79,21,Koma iye adachikana ndipo sanamvere
  79,22,Iye adapitirizabe kuchita zoipa
  79,23,Ndipo iye adaitana anthu ake onse ndipo anafuula mokweza
  79,24,"Nati: “Ine ndine Ambuye wanu wapamwamba mwamba.” Al-Naziat"
  79,25,Motero Mulungu adamugwetsera iye chilango chifukwa cha mau ake omaliza ndi oyamba
  79,26,Ndithudi mu izi muli phunziro lomveka kwa anthu oopa Mulungu
  79,27,Kodi inu ndinu ovuta kulenga kapena thambo la mlengalenga limene Mulungu adalilenga
  79,28,Iye analikweza m’mwamba ndi kulikonza bwino
  79,29,Usiku wake amaukuta ndi m’dima ndipo masana ake amatulutsa kuwala
  79,30,Ndipo pambuyo pake adalikulitsa dziko
  79,31,Ndipo anatulutsa madzi ndi msipu
  79,32,Ndipo adazika mapiri molimbika
  79,33,Chakudya cha phindu kwa inu ndi kwa zoweta zanu
  79,34,Koma pamene mavuto akulu akudza
  79,35,Tsiku limene munthu adzayamba kuganiza ntchito zake zonse
  79,36,Ndipo Gahena idzabweretsedwa pafupi kuti aliyense aione
  79,37,Ndipo kwa iye ophwanya malamulo
  79,38,Ndipo anasankha moyo wapadziko lino
  79,39,Ndithudi malo ake okhala ndi ku Gahena
  79,40,Koma kwa iwo amene amaopa kukaima pamaso pa Ambuye wake ndi machimo ndipo anali kudziletsa kuchita chifuniro chopanda pake
  79,41,Ndithudi adzakhala ku Paradiso
  79,42,Amakufunsa za nthawi imene chigumula chidzabwere
  79,43,Iwe siudziwa zoti unene china chili chonse
  79,44,Ndi Ambuye wako yekha amene amadziwa tsiku
  79,45,Iwe ndiwe mchenjezi chabe kwa iwo amene ali kuliopa tsikuli
  79,46,"Patsiku limene iwo adzachiona chigumula, kudzakhala ngati kuti iwo sanakhale padziko lapansi nthawi yaitali koma usiku umodzi kapena usana wokha"
  80,1,Iye anachita matsinya ndi kuyang’ana kumbali
  80,2,Chifukwa munthu wakhungu anadza kwa iye
  80,3,Ndipo iwe ungadziwe bwanji kuti mwina angadziyeretse
  80,4,Kapena iye adzalandira chenjezo ndipo chenjezo likanamupindulira kanthu kena
  80,5,Koma iye amene amadziyesa kuti sasowa kanthu
  80,6,Ameneyo ndiye amene uli naye ndi chidwi
  80,7,Kodi uli nazo chiani ngati iye sadziyeretsa
  80,8,Koma kwa iye amene amakuthamangira
  80,9,Ndipo iye amaopa
  80,10,Iwe siudamulabadire ayi
  80,11,Iyayi! Ndithudi chimenechi ndi chikumbutso
  80,12,Muloleni aliyense amene afuna kuti achilabadire
  80,13,Ichi chidalembedwa m’Buku la Mulungu lolemekezeka
  80,14,Loyeretsedwa ndi losungidwa bwino ndi loyera
  80,15,M’manja mwa Alembi
  80,16,Wolemekezeka ndipo womvera
  80,17,Atembereredwe munthu! Kodi ndi chiani chili kumuletsa kuthokoza
  80,18,Kodi Iye adamulenga kuchokera ku chiyani
  80,19,"Kuchokera ku dontho la umuna, Iye adamulenga ndipo adamukonza bwino"
  80,20,Ndipo Iye adamukonzera iye njira yapafupi
  80,21,Ndipo amamupha ndi kumusunga m’manda
  80,22,Ndithudi Iye adzamudzutsa monga momwe afunira
  80,23,"Iyayi, koma munthu sanachite zimene Iye adamulamulira"
  80,24,Mulekeni munthu kuti aganize za chakudya chake
  80,25,Kuti Ife timagwetsa mvula yambiri
  80,26,Ndipo timaphwanya nthaka
  80,27,"Ndipo Ife Al-Takwir\t641 timameretsa njere"
  80,28,Mphesa ndi Msipu
  80,29,"Mitengo ya mafuta, ndi mitengo ya tende"
  80,30,Ndi minda imene ili ndi mitengo yambiri
  80,31,Ndi mitengo ya zipatso ndi msipu
  80,32,Chakudya cha inu ndi ziweto zanu
  80,33,Koma pamene kulira kogonthetsa mkhutu kudzamveka
  80,34,Patsiku limene munthu adzakana m’bale wake
  80,35,Amai ake ndi bambo ake
  80,36,Mkazi wake ndi ana ake
  80,37,"Chifukwa aliyense patsiku limeneli, adzakhala otangwanika ndi mavuto ake"
  80,38,Patsiku limeneli padzakhala nkhope zambiri zowala
  80,39,Zosekerera ndi zachimwemwe chifukwa cha nkhani yabwino
  80,40,Ndipo pa tsikuli padzakhala nkhope zina zokutidwa ndi fumbi
  80,41,M’dima udzakuta iwo
  80,42,Awa adzakhala anthu osakhulupirira ndi ochita zoipa
  81,1,Pamene dzuwa lidzavundikiridwa
  81,2,Ndi pamene nyenyezi zidzagwa pansi
  81,3,Ndi pamene mapiri adzachotsedwa
  81,4,Ndi pamene ngamila zabele zizakhala zosasamalidwa
  81,5,Ndi nyama za m’tchire zidzasonkhanitsidwa pamodzi
  81,6,Ndi pamene nyanja zidzayatsidwa moto kapena zidzasefukira
  81,7,Ndi pamene mizimu idzakumanitsidwa ndi matupi awo
  81,8,"Ndi pamene mwana wa mkazi wa mng’ono, amene adaundilidwa wa moyo adzafunsidwa"
  81,9,Chifukwa chimene anamuphera
  81,10,Ndi pamene mabuku olembamo ntchito za munthu aliyense adzatulutsidwa
  81,11,Ndi pamene kumwamba kudzafafanizidwa ndi kuchotsedwa ku malo ake
  81,12,Ndi pamene Gahena idzatenthetsedwa kwambiri
  81,13,Ndi pamene Paradiso idzafikitsidwa pafupi
  81,14,Ndithudi munthu aliyense adzadziwa chimene adachita
  81,15,"Motero, ndithudi, Ine ndili kulumbira pali nyenyezi zimene zimalowa"
  81,16,Ndi pali maiko zimene zimayenda mofulumira ndi kudzibisa okha
  81,17,Ndi pali usiku pamene uchoka
  81,18,Ndipalim’mawapamenekulikucha
  81,19,Ndithudi awa ndi Mau a Mtumwi wolemekezeka
  81,20,"Mwini mphamvu amene amalemekezedwa ndi Ambuye, Mwini Mpando wa Chifumu"
  81,21,Amamveredwa ndi wokhulupirika
  81,22,Ndipo m’bale wanu uyu si wa misala ayi
  81,23,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iye adamuona iye mu mlengalenga"
  81,24,Iye sabisa zinthu zosaoneka
  81,25,Ndipo zimene alankhula sizochokera kwa Satana wotembereredwa
  81,26,Kodi inu muli kupita kuti
  81,27,Ndithudi ichi si china chilichonse ayi koma chikumbutso kwa anthu a mitundu yonse
  81,28,Kwa aliyense wa inu amene afuna kuyenda moongoka
  81,29,"Koma inu simungathe kutero pokhapokha ndi chifuniro cha Mulungu, Ambuye wa zolengedwe zonse"
  82,1,Pamene thambo lidzang’ambika
  82,2,Pamene nyenyezi zidzagwa ndi kubalalitsidwa
  82,3,Ndi pamene nyanja zikuluzikulu zidzaphulika
  82,4,Pamene manda adzatseguka
  82,5,Pamenepo Mzimu uliwonse udzadziwa chimene udatumiza ndi chimene udasiya m’mbuyo
  82,6,oh Iwe munthu! Kodi ndi chiyani chikukunamiza kuti usiye kutsatira malamulo a Ambuye wako Wolemekezeka
  82,7,Amene adakulenga iwe ndi kukukonza kuti uzioneka bwino monga mmene uonekeramu
  82,8,Ndi nkhope ina iliyonse imene idamukondweretsa anakulenga iwe
  82,9,Iyayi! Koma inu mukukana kuti kudzakhala tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,10,Koma pakati panu pali ena amene ali kukuyang’anirani
  82,11,Olemekezeka ndi odziwa kulemba
  82,12,Iwo amadziwa chilichonse chimene mumachita
  82,13,Ndithudi anthu onse angwiro adzakhala mu mtendere
  82,14,"Ndipo, ndithudi, anthu onse oipa adzakhala ku Gahena"
  82,15,Imene iwo adzalowako ndi kulawa malawi ake patsiku lachiweruzo
  82,16,Iwo sadzatha kuthawa ayi
  82,17,Kodi chidzakuuza ndi chiani za tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,18,Tinenanso kodi chidzakuuza ndi chiani za tsiku lachiweruzo
  82,19,Ndi tsiku limene mzimu uliwonse sudzatha kuthandiza wina aliyense ndipo Mulungu yekha ndiye amene adzaweruza
  83,1,Tsoka kwa iwo onse amene amagulitsa malonda awo monyenga
  83,2,Iwo amene amati ena akamawayesera zinthu amafuna kuti zikwanire muyeso wake
  83,3,Koma pamene iwo ayesa kapena awayesera anthu ena amawanyenga
  83,4,Kodi iwo saganiza kuti adzaukitsidwa kwa akufa
  83,5,Patsiku lalikulu
  83,6,Tsiku limene anthu a mitundu yonse adzaima pamaso pa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  83,7,Iyayi! Ndithudi chiwerengero cha anthu onse oipa chili mu Sijjin
  83,8,Kodi udzadziwa bwanji Sijjin ndi chiyani
  83,9,Ili ndi Buku lolembedwa
  83,10,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  83,11,Iwo amene amakana kuti kuli tsiku lachiweruzo
  83,12,Palibe wina amene amalikana tsikuli kupatula munthu wogona m’machimo
  83,13,"Pamene chivumbulutso chathu chinenedwa kwa iye, iye amati: “Izi ndizo nthano za anthu akale.”"
  83,14,Iyayi! Koma m’mitima mwawo ndi mokutidwa ndi zintchito zimene amachita
  83,15,Iyayi! Ndithudi iwo sadzaloledwa kuona Ambuye wawo pa tsikuli
  83,16,Ndipo iwo adzalowa ndi kulawa moto ku Gahena
  83,17,"Ndipo kudzanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Chimenechi ndicho chilango chija munkachinena kuti sichidzakhalako.”"
  83,18,Iyayi! Ndithudi chiwerengero cha anthu olungama chimasungidwa mu Illiyyun
  83,19,Kodi mudzadziwa bwanji kuti Illiyin wapamwambayo ndi chiyani
  83,20,"Ndi Al Mutaffifin\t645 Buku lochita kulembedwa"
  83,21,Limene limaonedwa ndi iwo okhawo amene ali kufupi ndi zofuna za Mulungu
  83,22,Ndithudi anthu onse olungama adzakhala ku malo a mtendere
  83,23,Atakhala pa mipando ya wofowofo ndipo ali kuyang’ana uku ndi uku
  83,24,Ndipo udzaona chisangalalo pa nkhope zawo
  83,25,Iwo adzapatsidwa kuti amwe vinyo weniweni amene sanatsegulidwepo
  83,26,"Womaliza wake adzakhala ndi fungo labwino ndipo pachifukwa cha ichi, aleke onse amene afuna kulimbikira kuti alimbike"
  83,27,Wosakanizidwa ndi madzi a Tasnim
  83,28,Kasupe amene anthu odala adzakhala ali kumwa
  83,29,"Ndithudi! Anthu amene amachita zoipa, anali kuwaseka anthu amene anakhulupirira"
  83,30,Ndi kumacheulana iwo akamadutsa pakati pawo
  83,31,Ndipo iwo amati akabwerera kwa anthu awo amabwera ali kunyoza
  83,32,"Ndipo amati akawaona iwo amati: “Ndithudi awa ndiwo anthu osochera.”"
  83,33,Pamene iwo sadalamulidwe kuti akhale owayang’anira
  83,34,Koma pa tsikuli anthu okhulupirira adzaseka anthu osakhulupirira
  83,35,Ali pa mipando yawofowofo ndi kumayang’ana
  83,36,"Kodi anthu osakhulupirira, sanalipidwe mphotho yawo molingana ndi ntchito zawo"
  84,1,Pamene thambo lidzang’ambika
  84,2,Ndipo limva ndi kumvera Ambuye wake ndipo ling’ambikadi
  84,3,Pamene nthaka idzatambasulidwa
  84,4,Ndi kutulutsa zonse zimene zinakwiriridwa m’kati mwake ndi kukhala yopanda kanthu
  84,5,Ndipo limva ndi kumvera Ambuye wake ndipo ling’ambikadi
  84,6,oh iwe munthu! Ndithudi iwe uli kubwerera kupita kwa Ambuye wako ndi ntchito zako. Kubwerera kotsimikizidwa. Motero udzakumana nazo
  84,7,Koma Iye amene adzapatsidwa Buku lake m’dzanja lamanja
  84,8,Adzawerengedwa mosavuta
  84,9,Ndipo adzabwerera kwa anthu ake ndi chisangalalo
  84,10,Koma iye amene adzapatsidwa buku lake kumbuyo kwake
  84,11,Iye adzalira
  84,12,Ndipo akalowa ku moto walawi – lawi ku Gahena
  84,13,Ndithudi iye adali wansangala pakati pa anthu ake
  84,14,Ndithudi iye anali kuganiza kuti sadzabwerera kwa Mulungu
  84,15,Inde! Ndithudi Ambuye wake anali kuona zonse zimene iye ankachita
  84,16,Ine ndilumbira pali kufiira kwa kulowa kwa dzuwa
  84,17,Ndi pali usiku ndi zonse zimene umabweretsa mu mdima
  84,18,Ndi pali mwezi pamene ufika pa chimake penipeni
  84,19,"Ndipo inu, ndithudi, mudzayenda kupita kutsogolo, kuchoka apa ndi kufika apo"
  84,20,Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani choti iwo alibe chikhulupiriro
  84,21,Ndipo pamene Korani ili kuwerengedwa kwa iwo sagwa pansi. Al-Buruj
  84,22,Iyayi! Koma anthu osakhulupirira amalikana
  84,23,Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa zinthu zonse zimene amasonkhanitsa
  84,24,Choncho auze iwo za chilango chowawa
  84,25,"Kupatula okhawo amene akhulupirira ndi kumachita ntchito zabwino, chifukwa iwo ali ndi malipiro opanda malire"
  85,1,Pali kumwamba kumene kuli nyenyezi zikulu zikulu
  85,2,Pali tsiku lolonjezedwa
  85,3,Pali tsiku la umboni ndi tsiku loperekedwa umboni
  85,4,wotembereredwa anali anthu amene anakumba ngalande
  85,5,Imene munali moto woyaka
  85,6,Pamene akhala moizungulira
  85,7,Ndipo iwo adachitira umboni pa zomwe amachitira anthu okhulupirira
  85,8,"Iwo analibe mlandu wina uliwonse ndi anthuwa kupatula kuti anali kukhulupirira mwa Mulungu mmodzi yekha, Mwini mphamvu zonse, Mwini kuyamikidwa"
  85,9,Mwini Ufumu wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi! Ndipo Mulungu ndi mboni pa chilichonse
  85,10,"Ndithudi onse amene adazunza amuna okhulupirira, ndi akazi okhulupilira ndipo salapa machimo awo, adzalandira chilango chowawa cha moto woyaka wa ku Gahena"
  85,11,Ndithu onse amene akhulupirira ndi kuchita ntchito zabwino adzakhala m’minda imene ili ndi mitsinje ya madzi oyenda. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu
  85,12,Ndithudi chilango cha Ambuye wako ndi chowawa
  85,13,Ndithudi Iye ndiye amene amayambitsa chilengedwe ndipo adzachibwereza patsiku louka kwa akufa
  85,14,Ndipo Iye ndi wokhululuka ndi wachikondi chodzadza
  85,15,"Mwini wake wa Mpando wachifumu, Wolemekezeka"
  85,16,Iye amachita chimene afuna
  85,17,Kodi iwe siudamve za asirikali
  85,18,A Farao ndi a Thamoud
  85,19,Iyayi! Koma anthu osakhulupirira amazikana
  85,20,Ndipo Mulungu amawazungulira onse
  85,21,Iyayi! Ili ndi Buku loyera la Korani
  85,22,Lolembedwa m’Buku lotetezedwa
  86,1,Pali kumwamba ndi pali Nyenyezi yowala
  86,2,Kodi chidzakudziwitsa kuti Nyenyezi yowala ndi chiani
  86,3,Ndi Nyenyezi yowala kothobwetsa maso
  86,4,Ndithudi moyo uliwonse uli ndi mtetezi wake
  86,5,Tamulekani munthu kuti aganize kuti adalengedwa kuchokera ku chiyani
  86,6,Iye adalengedwa kuchokera ku madzi otuluka
  86,7,Amene amatuluka kuchokera pakati pa pfupa la munsana ndi nthiti
  86,8,Ndithudi Iye ali ndi mphamvu zomudzutsa
  86,9,Pa tsiku limene zinthu zobisika zidzayesedwa
  86,10,Ndipo adzakhala wopanda mphamvu kapena womuthandiza
  86,11,Pali mtambo umene umapereka mvula kawiri kawiri
  86,12,Ndi pali dziko lapansi limene limang’ambika
  86,13,Ndithudi! Awa ndi mawu amene amasiyanitsa
  86,14,Si nthabwala ayi
  86,15,"Ndithudi iwo Al-A’la\t649 ali kukonza chiwembu"
  86,16,Ndipo Inenso ndili kukonza chiwembu
  86,17,Motero apatse nthawi anthu osakhulupirira. Ndipo chita nawo mwamtendere pa kanthawi kochepa
  87,1,Lemekeza dzina la Ambuye wako wapamwambamwamba
  87,2,Amene adalenga zonse ndi kuzikonza bwinobwino
  87,3,Amene adalamula tsogolo lawo ndi kuwatsogolera
  87,4,Amene amameretsa msipu
  87,5,Ndipo amausanduliza kukhala udzu ouma
  87,6,Tidzakuphunzitsa kulakatula chivumbulutso chathu ndipo sudzaiwala
